title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Zeiram
itunes:title: Weirdhouse Cinema: Zeiram
description:
In this episode of Weirdhouse Cinema, Rob and Joe discuss the 1991 Japanese sci-fi monster film Zeiram, in which a futuristic bounty hunter from space must hunt down a deadly alien renegade with the help of two hapless electricians.
